    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape, super dependable, and ready for its next adventure. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty won't let you down. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it feels!",
