    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, providing direct mechanical linkage and precise gear selection. The chassis has been reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to address common platform fatigue, and the suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers for improved lateral stability. The variable M differential lock ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle, maintaining excellent traction through technical apexes. With a documented service history focusing on valve clearances and rod bearing health, this M3 is a turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
