    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's honestly been such a dream to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable car that still looks and feels great on the road. I\u2019ve loved every mile in it, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love how smoothly it handles!",
