    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for purchase is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 straight-six engine. This unit features a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a complete VANOS overhaul and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The suspension has been upgraded with adjustable coilovers for sharpened turn-in response, while the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential ensures efficient power delivery. Though the finish shows honest patina from spirited use, the powertrain remains tight with a recent valve adjustment and fluid service. A true driver\u2019s specification optimized for performance and mechanical longevity.",
